{
  "stem": "26576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was terrible because we didn't know where we are going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like we were crossing-- it's only when we crossed the Ural Mountains, which was weeks and weeks after-- you know, there was no sanitation.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you needed to the toilet, when the train would stop, you would go [INAUDIBLE] and do it in the fields.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what we started to do-- we started like to exchange-- or rather if we could-- we learned quick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like we would come to a station, we would exchange like a jumper, my mother's jumper or that, for some food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this as far as I remember because I couldn't remember if we were given-- I know that [NON-ENGLISH] were given.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With peasants, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With people-- you know, it was a station with people, even if our Russian was nonexistent almost.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I saw that, so I said people were coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the typical thing in Russia because, later on, when we-- when it was the same thing, that people-- if they had some-- some people, this was their profession.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if they had some kind of food, they would go to the station, and they knew that trains will be coming with people from Vladivostok or somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would-- there will be an exchange of goods, you know, because money was of no importance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Money was paper that you couldn't do much with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's food that was number one, and for food, you were willing to give away things.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
